vote.title: Authorize acquisition of a drainage easement containing approximately 2,119 square feet of land from James L. Coon and Brad Cleveland located on Eustis Avenue near its intersection with Lakeland Drive for the Sanford Avenue Storm Drainage Relief System Project - Not to exceed $95,649.00 ($93,149.00 plus closing costs, and title expenses not to exceed $2,500.00) - Financing: 2024 Certificates of Obligation Fund
